{"tid":1208553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人對抗啦","createTime":"2019-06-12T09:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T14:43:13.000Z","uid":226824,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f774f73934947e72709f6e08381a93d35d4864a4","tid":1208553,"uid":226824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:44:51.000Z","msg":"點對抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身分證比人抄低哂<br />\n有哂記錄寫明係搞事份子<br />\n幾十年後中國接管返香港<br />\n政府查返你戶籍查地址耐唔耐就搵公安拍門<br />\n上門招呼你地<br />\n就算政府唔做野，所謂既香港警察到時歸順左大陸，都一定用私刑<br />\n上門打鳩你，摑你個仔兩巴輪你個女大米<br />\n到時投訴都冇得投訴<br />\n<br />\n有人話美國會收大陸皮<br />\nOk，當你可以打贏大陸<br />\n但係唔好唔記得<br />\n警察係美國都有好大權<br />\n到時又行私刑，用身分證查你戶籍<br />\n專登搜你個連登毒撚四眼仔<br />\n搜你身個陣試下郁，即刻開槍打你話你有攻擊性<br />\n合作唔郁既未拉返差館問話，打完一輪比你走囉<br />\n<br />\n奉勸大家，做人唔好去太盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只會增加仇恨到時比人秋後算帳<br />\n<br />\n香港人想對抗？唔移民就冇出路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw移民之前都要冇犯過法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人拉過就係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />注定留守香港"},{"pid":"2103475f70ae48291c1149f09c5a7100704aed93","tid":1208553,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:52:17.000Z","msg":"你條撚樣食屎啦仆街"},{"pid":"3589147a7da8538f29086cad068aac67014637dd","tid":1208553,"uid":226824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2103475f70ae48291c1149f09c5a7100704aed93","tid":1208553,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:52:17.000Z","msg":"你條撚樣食屎啦仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:55:39.000Z","msg":"Ching，忠言逆耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我明既"},{"pid":"d259ce07f4793c88b40fded979cac8a8393689e3","tid":1208553,"uid":226824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0dc5db8c4b2d56f56cf9d7234812613b47c4ff5","tid":1